title: STANLEY S9500 Black/Yellow 1" x 10' Ratchet Straps - Light Cargo Hauling (900 lb Break Strength), 4 Pack
description: The STANLEY 4-Pack Ratchet Straps are perfect for light cargo transporting including securing ladders, lawn equipment, your bicycle in your truck or trailer, or securing a tarp over the campsite wood pile. These 1" by 10' weather-resistant webbed straps feature reinforced stitching for safely securing cargo with ease.
